---
title: Hearty Potato & Coconut Curry with Brown Rice & Cashews
description: With its gentle warming heat and colourful veggies, a rich and creamy Indian curry is a favourite meal
for good reason! Whip up this veggie version with turnip, carrot and potato, plus wholesome brown rice
that'll leave you embracing a modern classic.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
